::Prowl/Striker::

One of Prowl's eyebrows raises as Iron Raptor leaves him in charge and tells 
him to put up the scans. She was good at giving orders, but he wasn't under 
her command, Striker was his commander.

He shruggs. He'd tell her later. He turns to bring up the scans as her 
transmission reaches his comm-link. He turns and looks at Striker, realizing 
it was too late to stop him.

He swears under his breath, turning to face Sniper. "Yeah, go ahead," he 
says. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker frowns at Cyber Claws responce. "Primal is not on the planet," he 
says, you should know that, you've been here for quite a while...."
